          <name xml:lang="en">price</name>
          <unitName xml:lang="en">EUR2005</unitName>
          <comment xml:lang="en">The price data was collected from Alibaba for two beverage cartons suitable for fresh milk packaging. The average price of the products was 0.045 $/pc. The price was converted to EUR based on the annual exchange rates published by the European Central Bank (https://sdw.ecb.europa.eu/quickview.do?SERIES_KEY=120.EXR.A.USD.EUR.SP00.A, last accessed on 2022-02-15) and adjusted for inflation relative to 2005 using the producer price index (PPI) of the euro area, published by eurostat (https://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/databrowser/view/STS_INPP_A__custom_6416181/default/table?lang=en, last accessed on 2022-05-04).</comment>
